ay trip to Seville","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0064_day_trip_seville_532854259_rfis_0217_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/portugal/algarve/general/fao0064_day_trip_seville_532854259_rfis_0217_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.10746,"longitude":-8.676301},"summary":"Stroll down the cobbled streets of the Santa Cruz quarter, making your way to the Alcazar Palace drinking in the scent of orange blossom, or climb the steps in the Giralda tower for the view across the city. ","url":"/poi/algarve/day-trip-to-seville","category":"Activities"},{"code":"","title":"Ilha da Culatra","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5031_ilha_da_culatra_1016_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/faro/fao5031_ilha_da_culatra_1016_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":36.98891,"longitude":-7.833611},"summary":"Grab your beach parasol and head to Ilha da Culatra for the day. ","url":"/poi/algarve/ilha-da-culatra","category":"Sights"},{"code":"FAO0243","title":"Loulé Carnival","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0243_loule_carnival_517302360_rfis_1117_01.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/destinations/poi/fao poi/fao0243_loule_carnival_517302360_rfis_1117_01.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.1389,"longitude":-8.022492},"summary":"If you want to explore a lesser-known side of the Algarve, Loul&eacute; is a great place to start. ","url":"/poi/algarve/loule-carnival","category":"Activities"},{"code":"FAO0144","title":"Mercado de Loulé","images":{"thumbnail":"/-/media/fao_market_of_loule_926778726_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg","heroImage":"/-/media/fao_market_of_loule_926778726_getty_rgb-136-dpi-for-web.jpg"},"location":{"description":"Algarve, Portugal","latitude":37.1385422,"longitude":-8.02216148},"summary":"Discover Mercado de Loul&eacute;, an incredible covered market in this traditional town